long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: "Improve your typing skills and have fun with our Word Typer Game Chrome extension. This extension provides an engaging way to enhance your typing speed and accuracy. Blast your way through an arcade-style game while typing words and sentences. Whether you're a beginner or an advanced typist, the Word Typer Game is designed to help you practice and improve your typing skills. Get ready to level up your typing abilities while enjoying an exciting gaming experience right in your browser."
